PROGRAM REQUIREMENTS
----------
	1. Ruby >= 1.8
	2. Ruby Gems
	3. Mechanize (Ruby Gem)
	4. Hpricot (Ruby Gem)
	5. Linux environment with specefied libraries
		a. ...
		b. all unpacking libraries
		c. ...



1. Install Ruby
	a. In Linux (Ubuntu/Debian) : apt-get install ruby
	b. In Windows : http://link-to-ruby-download-page
2. Install Ruby Gems
3. Hpricot
